OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy at
OL,6,Ffirst with a few evening showers and a
OL,7,Fchance of a few thunderstorms pushing
OL,8,Feastwards. Gusty winds with hail and
OL,9,Flightning possible. Rain then clearing
OL,10,Fto leave a dry, warm and humid night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FVery hot and humid on Tuesday
OL,13,Fwith strong sunshine and lighter winds
OL,14,Fthan Monday. High humidity will
OL,15,Fintensify the heat making it feel
OL,16,Funcomfortable.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
